<h3>Service Components</h3>
<p>
    The following components provide the service interaction to support the service-oriented architecture (SOA).
    A single WCF service is used that encapsulates all service messaages exposed by system modules.
    Common Service Locator is used to inject concrete service providers to interfaces throughout the system, with the unofficial adapter providing integration with Structuremap.
</p>
